Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)\c&H00ffff&}あ… あれは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,898)\c&H00ffff&}私のエサです
